  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, do not give the genealogy of my fathers in this part of my record;",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.892,
      "end": 8.307,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither at any time shall I give it",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 8.487,
      "end": 11.134,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after upon these plates which I am writing;",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 11.314,
      "end": 15.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it is given in the record which has been kept by my father;",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 15.72,
      "end": 18.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I do not write it in this work.",
      "verse": "6:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 18.815,
      "end": 22.577,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For it is enough for me to say that we are descendants of Joseph.",
      "verse": "6:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 23.257,
      "end": 24.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it matters not to me",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 25.062,
      "end": 29.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I am particular to give a full account of all the things of my father,",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 29.84,
      "end": 32.348,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they cannot be written upon these plates,",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 32.528,
      "end": 34.293,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I desire the room",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 34.473,
      "end": 36.841,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I may write of the things of God.",
      "verse": "6:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 37.521,
      "end": 41.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the fullness of my intent is that I may persuade men to come",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 41.277,
      "end": 42.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to the God of Abraham,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 43.175,
      "end": 44.986,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the God of Isaac,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 45.166,
      "end": 46.838,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the God of Jacob,",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 47.018,
      "end": 48.318,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and be saved.",
      "verse": "6:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 48.998,
      "end": 52.713,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, the things which are pleasing to the world I do not write,",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 52.893,
      "end": 55.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but the things which are pleasing to God",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 55.441,
      "end": 57.717,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to those who are not of the world.",
      "verse": "6:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 58.397,
      "end": 61.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, I shall give commandment to my seed,",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 61.271,
      "end": 64.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they shall not occupy these plates with things",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 64.33,
      "end": 67.116,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which are not of worth to the children of men.",
      "verse": "6:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    }
  ]
}